Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.02,0:00:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是模特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮肤也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我也是完美的帅哥状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之就是文武双全才色兼备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上还有比我更完美的男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就练前桥  平板撑抬腿和俯卧撑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想自己几岁了老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都几岁了  给我注意一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真君是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是小学五年级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你睡糊涂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  真君  不能欺负女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浅江姐姐的女儿春香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浅江  姨妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  春香是真君的表妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好一年没见了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春香…春香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这名字好像听过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我才刚瘦下来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好吃 好喝 好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政宗哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个胖嘟嘟布丁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  一年不见长得太像萝莉老太婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不  那个  长大了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么把妈妈弄哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什么啊  你个不孝子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政宗君和千夏关系还是那么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姨妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想给春香也生个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也完全没问题哦  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那就得加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要个哥哥那就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么样也是姐妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过怎么会这么像  我家老太婆是怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先换身衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这么放着不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再靠近点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道去报警了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姨妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是浅江姨妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是稍微认真了一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真?  认真是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么认真了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浅江姐姐也来让千夏拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶  一起来一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化妆就能化成这样真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化妆?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你管这叫化妆?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说我家的萝莉老太婆也是化妆?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人真可怕  完全不敢想象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥真傻啊  妈妈那是天然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样还是觉得可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  真正的妈妈是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁才是真正的妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我  看我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  春花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为真君的女朋友  努力长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表兄妹是可以结婚的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼光是不错  值得称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已经有约在先了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  说太直了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等你的约定取消了就到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁一族的女性都很坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮得到你说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海水的咸味浓得都快呛到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到今年也能来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好感谢邀请我们来的爱姬小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  感觉又有好玩的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到了  准备一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到纲手岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一年不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  由井崎小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  你还是那样呢  可爱的男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的男孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有爱姬小姐邀请来的各位  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各方面都请多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年那个超清爽的男生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分手了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是刚分手的时期吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱姬小姐  请振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上比那个男生好的人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  不管是牢骚还是怨念都朝我倾诉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可惜了  政宗君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没那件事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  原因是出轨了吗  还是家暴?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两边都是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和谁出轨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对谁家暴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史上最笨的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我也是完美状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天锻炼的完美身材
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐姿走姿都是那般美丽动人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那如太阳般耀眼的帅哥气场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直完美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被自己迷倒一头撞在电线杆上了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还流血了?  脑震荡?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那是有多自恋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是笨蛋吗  笨蛋中的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才在家里修养啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  哎呀应该说万幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他能尽快恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那笨蛋我还是尽快卖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就接手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个  都不知道什么叫开玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  还以为是认真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一下  就试穿一下  这件泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁君  为什么要抛下我一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对很适合的啊  可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  随时都行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  是成长期吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  我可和以前不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  今天天气…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉  吉乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在  爱姬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了  能拿点吃的给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃的还请自己去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉乃也变强硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从发梢开始梳比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀嚯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事  当然是女生夜谈会啦夜谈会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定要彻夜聊天呀  难得来海边  又是晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候果然还是要有点心和恋爱话题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  恋爱话题  比如喜欢的男生类型之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个先不说  比如只有现在才能说得的烦恼之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  不管是恋爱话题或烦恼都可以跟我聊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聚到一起的话果然还是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学习
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  都到高三了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要为上大学的考试做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是汉字练习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒不够喝了喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么撇下人家自己玩得那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十八九岁的人也好意思自称女生?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老太婆也太拼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日礼物要求别人送戒指也太沉重了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛肉盖饭就足够了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱只不过是自相情愿和误解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从梦里醒来只不过是早晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  爱姬  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个帅哥只不过是因为长得帅才交往的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是胖子才不会交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  如果是胖子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话只要他身体健康就不会介意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都会交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才移开视线了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你是个颜控吧  真是可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们听听你的解释吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁君  救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还行吧  你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么  玩得挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心别人伤势如何  有没有又撞到哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是宽心的很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寂寞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然寂寞了  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是纲手岛带回来的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  辛苦你了  玩得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你不是休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去纲手岛算休息日加班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是  我明白你穿着平时的衣服比较安心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便挑一套吧  穿穿看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种太成熟了  不适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说什么呢  亲姐妹的东西怎么会不适合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不太对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你站着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话要见血哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刘海还是再剪一点比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是拷问…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睁开眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你天生的跑腿气质没法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今天是难得的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犒劳下自己好好去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是为了能达成爱姬小姐的需求  没有带过这么小的包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能第一时间赶过去  总是穿着平底的鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的指甲也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合您的口味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么并不觉得开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那边看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  因为我就算变得再任性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的东西始终还是无法到手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去帮你要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗  刚才那女生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  哪个  有看到这样的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.99,0:21:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  你这孩子真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也觉得有点开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定变得更漂亮点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是拿出点干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得更漂亮  成为一个好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他喜欢上我  再甩掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爱姬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子也会露出那种表情呀
